      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ecef3e76-32b1-11e3-9a82-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
