      "date": "2013-10-21 15:15:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nYou get two lines returned to you with this modification:\n\n# df -P /lustre/scratch | awk '{print $5}' | sed 's/%//g' | grep -v Use\nCapacity\n5\n\nI think you want \"grep -v Capacity\" instead of \"grep -v Use\"?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
